{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Device Orientation Events 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code> 为 web 开发者提供了关于设备的位置和方向的改变速度的信息。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>警告：</strong> 目前，Firefox 和 Chrome 处理坐标的方式不同。使用时要多加注意。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.devicemotionevent\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.DeviceMotionEvent()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>创建一个新的 <code>DeviceMotionEvent</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.acceleration\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>提供了设备在 X,Y,Z 轴方向上加速度的对象。加速度的单位为 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.accelerationincludinggravity\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>提供了设备在 X,Y,Z 轴方向上带重力的加速度的对象。加速度的单位为 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.rotationrate\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.rotationRate</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>提供了设备在 alpha、beta、gamma 轴方向上旋转的速率的对象。旋转速率的单位为度每秒。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.interval\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.interval</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示从设备获取数据的间隔时间，单位是毫秒。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'devicemotion'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>acceleration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' m/s2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/#devicemotion","title":"DeviceOrientation Event Specification"}],"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events/Detecting_device_orientation\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Detecting device orientation (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\">Orientation and motion data explained</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"DeviceMotionEvent 为 web 开发者提供了关于设备的位置和方向的改变速度的信息。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参